title: 340 Wife Lovers - 3 Pack
description:
Essential Pack - Black, Blue, White

Pack 1 - All Black

Pack 2 - Olive, Brown, Black

Pack 4 - Black, White, Heather Grey

Pack 5 - Black, Heather Grey, Oatmeal 

MATERIAL: 95% Cotton 5% Lycra.

FIT: Fitted. Compression Like fitting. Size Up.

DESIGN: The wife lover tanks are here. These are nothing like your typical wife beater. These are made with very premium fabric and will last you a long time! A modern touch on the old beaters. These come in a pack of 3 and multiple color options. Made with stretchy cotton and lycra fabric. They hug the body like a glove and form perfectly to your body.

MODEL: The model in the second photo is wearing a size XXL. Weight: 250lb Height: 6'1.
